msgid "— Small hotspots are easy to miss. Methodically explore each screen."
msgstr "— Les petits points chauds sont faciles à rater. Explorer méthodiquement chaque écran."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_bass.html.heex:92
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Some puzzle sequences are complex and easy to get stuck in."
